00:31:19.520 --> 00:31:24.520
So Lord, we thank you so much for what you've done for us in Jesus.

455
00:31:24.520 --> 00:31:30.520
I pray that you would help us to look away from our sinfulness to his righteousness

456
00:31:30.520 --> 00:31:33.520
and his name we pray. Amen.

